<br>
Massivly Multiplayer Online Role Playing Game. <br>
these guys from NB that run around with 5 other people killing evrything - how 'massively multiplayer' is that? And role-playing? A person that Role Plays their character on EQ is very rare indeed. We are the people who will be the future of Karana - these 'bullys' as yall put will get bored eventually and move on and new bullys will come and be morons. the way things are - some people are born morons. <br>
<br>
Do people start a guild because they want to be powerful? Power mad people? NO - they start them because they want their game to be a better game - to really do something - i started a guild because of this reason and Haemish and Qamgine and Niann and all these other GL's out there probably did it for the same reason too.<br>
<br>
My guild disbanded recently so im going to help any guild that needs me, help the KGC and help the game by making it a better place - more fun and generally fairer. This game could be much better. There could be channels for every needs - we have trade and there are serverwide class-specific channels going - but more could exist - like one for help getting your corpse or one for getting people to clear the camp you are trying to clear before you can solo it. A server where everybody helps each oher would be a good thing, but sadly almost impossible. BUT we can try and at least get a solid community of people that do fun things to make the game fun - all these arguments about uberosity (cool word huh?) and stuff like that - does it really mean anything? Oooo nooo they killed what we were going to kill. maybe holding up your raid by a week...it may be a pain but these people will enjoy causing all that kinda s**t and messing it up. <br>
<br>
We may remember Haemish for doing KCoG and starting great things, but we are also remembering the trouble causers, the morons, and do we really want to remember them? Try ignoring the fools - disband them exclude them and then ignor them. Dont start a zone wide argument about all this - they enjoy it.<br>
<br>
Lets just stick together and spread KCoG's and KGC's word and for gawds sake do some lower lvl raids for fun like a BB raid with nobody over lvl 2 (i think a CB version of that was done not long ago) or maybe have a race or a game of chess using toons or a meeting to discuss things that have happened. <br>
<br>
The game is MASSIVELY MULTIPLAYER and we should work together to make what we pay for worth much more than we play. And i do wish Sony would let us buy houses/guildhalls for in game money and things like that. Plane of building maybe? (if we get a biiig petition do you think theyd add it over time) Im no expert in these kind of things but this is my opinion and i dont take many things seriously but this is something i feel rather strongly about and i belive that we could do this. <br>
<br>
Garrbut Windhammer 52nd Mystic<br>
Lighten up. Get a Pegasus feather cloak <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.showMessageRange?topicID=108.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.showPrevMessage?topicID=108.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.showNextMessage?topicID=108.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=108.topic&index=22><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/far_east/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.emailToFriend?topicID=108.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.threadControl?topicID=108.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/far_east/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=108.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=108.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of r